{
  "text": "The resulting tools include machine translators (Rivera-Trigueros 2022; Roxas et al. 2008), automated essay scorers (Landauer 2003), document summarizers (Koh et al. 2022; Mridha et al. 2021), paraphrasing tools (Roe & Perkins 2022), predictive text (Garay-Vitoria & Abascal 2006), story generators (Callaway & Lester 2002; Kybartas & Bidarra 2017), and conversational systems (Kasirzadeh & Gabriel 2023; Schöbel et al. 2023)."
}